{"tid":650046,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"監控新境界   中國推「腦電波監測帽」掌控人心","createTime":"2018-05-02T04:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T04:11:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c8aacf55f5919b393c01ac5c7cef2433e56f4896","tid":650046,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2411824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2411824&d=nRHBUVZHhqwhhyqBOnRgtE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=5578b34c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2411824&h=a44e2e1d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2411824</a><br />\n<br />\n繼DNA採集與人臉辨識後，中國當局監控人民的天網又增添一項新神器－「腦電波監控」技術，外媒指出，目前中國各省已有許多工廠、國有企業及軍隊員工的腦電波受當局監控，「以維持社會穩定」。<br />\n<br />\n外媒舉例，中國杭州中恒電器公司現已全面實施腦電波監控技術，員工在生產線上製作電信元件時，均被要求配戴一頂有相關裝置的帽子，以對其腦電波加以監控。管理人員將可透過數據蒐集，即時感知工人情緒是否有異常狀況，進一步調整生產進度，以提高整體工作效率。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，由中國政府資助，寧波大學研發的「Neuro Cap」技術，目前已在中國境內被十幾間工廠及企業廣泛使用，這種裝置常被裝設在帽子上，將配戴者的腦電波以數據形式發送至電腦，再由AI透過演算法來探測諸如抑鬱、焦慮或憤怒等情緒起伏，最終達成控管情緒的結果。<br />\n<br />\n對此，北京師範大學管理心理學教授喬治安表示，這項技術雖可提高工作效率，進而帶給企業更高的競爭力，但也可能會被當局濫用，藉以控制人民的思想及侵犯其隱私，「這種作法有如『思想警察』」，喬治安直言，「人腦監測已將侵犯隱私帶到一個新的境界」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffae6202179a59380029c28f5701c88e40aa31a","tid":650046,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:01:11.000Z","msg":"Yuri"},{"pid":"894be68d8e581a9eb5d4978d875f8763a57bd2b4","tid":650046,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:02:13.000Z","msg":"係咪抄yuri<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3b11c2bc108c3b9ad8841e29043c97777a6aab","tid":650046,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:02:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6983f331c285ef48812005fc9ad16f30745a54d7","tid":650046,"uid":156005,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:05:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>但是麻省理工科技評論對這項技術宣稱的效果不以為然，認為使用腦電圖透過皮膚進行腦部掃描效果仍然非常有限，且檢測到的訊號與人類情感之間的關係尚不清楚。南華早報報導指稱國家電網浙江電力公司可以因此增加 20 億元人民幣莉利潤，「非常令人懷疑」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09f0b2e0c2c5bc5b1b8346d3faa6e18309b4f17","tid":650046,"uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/tfscom/i4/382040880/TB1ntB1SFXXXXXVXXXXXXXXXXXX_!!1-item_pic.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Ftfscom%2Fi4%2F382040880%2FTB1ntB1SFXXXXXVXXXXXXXXXXXX_%21%211-item_pic.gif&h=c064c4fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f5f660f17f5030e01ffa17e79a3a5c9988049c4","tid":650046,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"地獄鬼國,無限中出SM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316f70e6053e6d98a9d4d23f1e966cab20bec5b0","tid":650046,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:11:17.000Z","msg":"所以我幾時都話黃種人最幸福"},{"pid":"be2c7f39b9cd5221928bb80f8e5a9be7be06dde3","tid":650046,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:12:25.000Z","msg":"Psycho-Pass成真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafa67a9332f8a3b0f6f71216298965e1b6644c4","tid":650046,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"316f70e6053e6d98a9d4d23f1e966cab20bec5b0","tid":650046,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:11:17.000Z","msg":"所以我幾時都話黃種人最幸福"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:13:31.000Z","msg":"成班黃種彊屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeff2d2fcb9b4bed31e5b2a1e376797